tip.text: Home cooked food specially made after taking your preferences and choices. They have Indian, Sri Lankan and American food. Great service.
Worst North Indian food in Singapore.  Degraded so badly over the years.  Especially the Punjabi dishes.  Amritsari fish was soaked in plan batter and fried without any garlic etc.
The wine and the food don't compensate for the lack of washrooms and toilets.  Singapore Airlines is good but  acts funny in simple things like these.
